function imasgrep(){

   ## idol_ymlã‹ã‚‰ç›´æ¥æƒ…å ±ã‚’å–å¾—ã—ã€idolã®ç·æ•°ã‚’å–å¾—
    GIRLS_ALL_NUM=$(cat $IDOL_YML | grep -E idol_id | tr -d "\""  |tr -d " "| wc -l )
    GIRLS_ALL_NUM=$(expr $GIRLS_ALL_NUM - 1)

   ## idol_idæ¯ã«ãƒ•ãƒ«ãƒãƒ¼ãƒ ã‚’é…åˆ—ã«å…¥ã‚Œã¦ã„ã
    GIRLS_NAME_LIST=($(cat $IDOL_YML | grep -E idol_id\|family:\|given:\|aka: | tr -d "\""  |tr -d " "| \
    awk -F":" '$1=="idol_id"{i=$2}$1=="family"{a[i]=$2}$1=="given"{b[i]=$2}$1=="aka"{a[i]=$2}END\
               {for(j = 1; j <= i; j++){printf ("%s%s ",a[j],b[j])}}'))
    
    TMP_DIR=$(mktemp -d)
    FILE_NAME=${FILE##*/}
 #   echo "FILE_NAME" $FILE_NAME  # debug

    # standard-in 
	if [ -p /dev/stdin ] && [ $FLAG_f -eq "1" ]; then     # ãƒ•ã‚¡ã‚¤ãƒ«ã®æ–‡å­—ã«æ¨™æº–å…¥åŠ›ã‚’åŠ ãˆã¦å‡¦ç†ã™ã‚‹
	    cp  $FILE $TMP_DIR/$FILE_NAME.swp
	    cat - >> $TMP_DIR/$FILE_NAME.swp
	elif [ -p /dev/stdin ] && [ $FLAG_f -eq "0" ] ;then   # æ¨™æº–å‡ºåŠ›ã®ã¿
	    cat - > $TMP_DIR/$FILE_NAME.swp
	#elif [ -p /dev/stdin ] && [ $FLAG_f -eq "1" ] ;then   # ãƒ•ã‚¡ã‚¤ãƒ«ã®ã¿
	elif [ $FLAG_f -eq "1" ] ;then   # ãƒ•ã‚¡ã‚¤ãƒ«ã®ã¿
	    cp  $FILE $TMP_DIR/$FILE_NAME.swp
        else 
            echo "Please Option \"[-f FILENAME]\" "   
            exit 1 
	fi 

    cd $TMP_DIR
    if [ $FLAG_n -eq "1" ] ;then

        ## å¯¾è±¡ã‚¢ã‚¤ãƒ‰ãƒ«ã®idol_id ã‚’å–å¾—ã™ã‚‹
        for i in `seq 0 $GIRLS_ALL_NUM`;do
#            j=$(expr $i + 1); echo "idol_id:"$j"=" ${GIRLS_NAME_LIST[$i]}  ; j=$(expr $i - 1) #debug
#            echo "NAME =" ${NAME} #debug
                if [ "${GIRLS_NAME_LIST[$i]}" = "${NAME}" ] ; then
                    j=$(expr $i + 1)
                    ## YMLã‚’ãƒ‘ãƒ¼ã‚¹å‡¦ç†ã—ãŸã‚‚ã®ã‚’åˆ©ç”¨ã—ã¦ã€å¯¾è±¡ã‚¢ã‚¤ãƒ‰ãƒ«ã®æƒ…å ±å–å¾—
                    #NAME_ID=$(parse_yaml $IDOL_YML  |grep idol_id|grep \"$j\" |cut -d"_" -f1)
                    #IDOL_COLOR=$(parse_yaml $IDOL_YML  |grep ${NAME_ID} |grep color |cut -d"\"" -f2)   	#[31må¤©æµ·æ˜¥é¦™[m
		    sed -i -e "s/${GIRLS_NAME_LIST[i]}/\\\e[31m${GIRLS_NAME_LIST[i]}\\\e[m/g"  $FILE_NAME.swp
                fi
        done

    else
        for i in `seq 0 $GIRLS_ALL_NUM`;do
#            j=$(expr $i + 1); echo "idol_id:"$j"=" ${GIRLS_NAME_LIST[$i]}  ; j=$(expr $i - 1) #debug
                   #j=$(expr $i + 1)
                    ## YMLã‚’ãƒ‘ãƒ¼ã‚¹å‡¦ç†ã—ãŸã‚‚ã®ã‚’åˆ©ç”¨ã—ã¦ã€å¯¾è±¡ã‚¢ã‚¤ãƒ‰ãƒ«ã®æƒ…å ±å–å¾—
                    #NAME_ID=$(parse_yaml $IDOL_YML  |grep idol_id|grep \"$j\" |cut -d"_" -f1)
                    #IDOL_COLOR=$(parse_yaml $IDOL_YML  |grep ${NAME_ID} |grep color |cut -d"\"" -f2)

                    sed -i -e "s/${GIRLS_NAME_LIST[i]}/\\\e[32m${GIRLS_NAME_LIST[i]}\\\e[m/g"  $FILE_NAME.swp
        done  
    fi
   
  # Defalt Output 
    while read -r line ;do  # -r ã‚¨ã‚¹ã‚±ãƒ¼ãƒ—ã‚’èª­ã¿è¾¼ã¿ãŸã‚ã«å¿…è¦
        echo -e ""$line""
    done < $FILE_NAME.swp

rm -rf $TMP_DIR

}


# echo function
function imasecho (){
    if [ $FLAG_P -eq "0" ] && [ $FLAG_m -eq "0" ] ; then
        P_NAME="ãƒ—ãƒ­ãƒ‡ãƒ¥ãƒ¼ã‚µãƒ¼"
	MESSAGE="ã‚¢ã‚¤ãƒã‚¹"
    elif [ $FLAG_P -eq "0" ]  && [ $FLAG_m -eq "1" ] ; then
        P_NAME="ãƒ—ãƒ­ãƒ‡ãƒ¥ãƒ¼ã‚µãƒ¼"
    elif [ $FLAG_P -eq "1" ]  && [ $FLAG_m -eq "0" ] ; then
	MESSAGE="ã‚¢ã‚¤ãƒã‚¹"
    fi

    echo "$P_NAME"'ã•ã‚“ï¼ '"$MESSAGE"'ã§ã™ã‚ˆï¼'"$MESSAGE"'ï¼'
}

